---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Ramps | Freedom Mobility NY"
  description="Custom ramp solutions in Rochester, Buffalo & Syracuse. Portable, modular, and permanent ramps installed by experts. Free in-home consultations."
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16">
    <nav class="text-sm mb-6 text-slate-500">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-slate-700">Home</a> <span class="mx-1">/</span> 
      <span class="text-slate-700">Ramps</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-10">
      <div>
        <span class="text-sky-600 font-semibold tracking-wider text-sm">SAFE ACCESS FOR EVERY HOME</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter mt-3 mb-6">Ramps</h1>

        <div class="prose prose-lg text-slate-700">
          <p>
            When it comes to finding the right ramp, you deserve expert guidance and personalized solutions. 
            Freedom Mobility NY offers free in-home consultations to ensure you receive a ramp tailored to your needs.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether you need a portable ramp for temporary use or a permanent ramp for your home, we provide a wide range of 
            options designed for durability, safety, and ease of use.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-slate-900 hover:bg-black text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl inline-flex font-semibold">Request a Free Ramp Consultation</a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Types of ramps we offer:</h3>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li>• Portable folding ramps</li>
            <li>• Threshold ramps</li>
            <li>• Modular aluminum ramps</li>
            <li>• Wooden permanent ramps</li>
            <li>• Wheelchair & scooter ramps</li>
            <li>• Custom length & configurations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <img src="/images/ramp_flag.jpeg" alt="Access ramp with American flag" class="rounded-3xl border shadow-sm w-full" loading="lazy" width="1200" height="630" decoding="async" />
        <p class="text-xs text-center mt-3 text-slate-500">Safe, code-compliant ramp solutions installed by our team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16">
    <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 text-sm">
      <strong>Our process:</strong> We measure your entry points, discuss usage (daily, seasonal, etc.), and recommend the safest, most cost-effective solution. 
      Installation is quick and clean. All ramps meet ADA guidelines where applicable.
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
